  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为在线问卷系统绘制一张上下文图，核心是一个让管理员创建问卷、受访者通过社交媒体链接参与回答的系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sistema",
        "admin",
        "respondente",
        "redes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我理解为：管理员负责后台管理，普通用户作为受访者通过社交媒体的分享链接进入系统填写问卷。这两个角色都需要明确区分对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "admin",
        "respondente",
        "redes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，受访者主要是被动通过Facebook、Instagram、Twitter这些渠道接触到问卷的，不是直接访问我们系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "respondente",
        "redes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我把外部系统定义为\"Redes Sociais\"，包含这几个主流平台，主要承担问卷的分发扩散功能。系统本体叫\"Sistema de Questionarios Online\"，可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "redes",
        "sistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，描述里要突出它能支撑大规模数据收集和结果汇总。另外，我们用了CDN来加速静态资源加载，这个也得画上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sistema",
        "cdn"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "CDN是外部系统对吧？它只给受访者提供静态内容，不涉及管理员的操作路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cdn",
        "respondente",
        "admin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，管理员走常规HTTP接口，受访者打开问卷页面时，JS、CSS这些静态资源走CDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cdn",
        "respondente",
        "admin",
        "sistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出四个外部/人物节点：Respondente、Administrador、Redes Sociais、CDN，以及核心的Sistema de Questionarios Online。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "respondente",
        "admin",
        "redes",
        "cdn",
        "sistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Respondente的描述我再精确一下：\"Pessoa que responde as pesquisas atraves de links em redes sociais\"，强调他们是通过社交链接进来的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "respondente",
        "redes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，已更新。Administrador那边是\"Usuario que cria pesquisas e visualiza resultados\"，这样对比清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "admin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "现在来梳理关系：Respondente到Sistema是\"Responde pesquisas\"，协议HTTP；Administrador到Sistema是\"Gerencia pesquisas e visualiza resultados\"，也是HTTP。这两条对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "respondente",
        "admin",
        "sistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，都是标准HTTP。Sistema还要指向Redes Sociais，表示生成分享链接，关系描述用\"Links compartilhados\"合适吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sistema",
        "redes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "合适，我加上。CDN到Respondente是\"Entrega conteudo estatico\"，这条是单向的，不需要返回箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cdn",
        "respondente"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，CDN和Sistema之间需要画关系吗？CDN的内容是我们提前部署上去的，不是实时从Sistema拉取。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cdn",
        "sistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "明白了，那我不画CDN和Sistema之间的连线，避免误解为实时回源。CDN作为独立外部系统只服务Respondente。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cdn",
        "sistema",
        "respondente"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Redes Sociais的描述补充为\"Facebook, Instagram, Twitter - divulgacao das pesquisas\"，把具体平台和用途都带上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "redes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已更新。CDN的描述定为\"Distribuicao de conteudo estatico\"，Sistema的描述包含创建问卷、大规模收集、结果汇总三层能力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cdn",
        "sistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Sistema的描述再调整一下语序：\"Permite criar pesquisas, coletar respostas em escala e visualizar resultados sumarizados\"，把功能递进关系理清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，已修正。现在检查所有关系：Respondente→Sistema（HTTP）、Admin→Sistema（HTTP）、Sistema→Redes（分享链接）、CDN→Respondente（静态内容）。共四条关系线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "respondente",
        "admin",
        "sistema",
        "redes",
        "cdn"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "数量对了。再确认一下Respondente和Redes Sociais之间不需要直接连线？他们确实是通过Redes上的链接跳转，但那个点击行为发生在Redes平台内部。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "respondente",
        "redes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解，不画直接连线。Respondent在Redes上看到链接，点击后跳转到Sistema，这个流转用Sistema→Redes的反向关系已经能表达分发逻辑了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "respondente",
        "redes",
        "sistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后确认所有元素类型：Respondente和Administrador是Person，Redes Sociais和CDN是System_Ext，Sistema是System。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "respondente",
        "admin",
        "redes",
        "cdn",
        "sistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部核对完毕，类型正确。图示已完整呈现在线问卷系统的上下文边界和外部依赖。",
